OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy across the region overnight
OL,7,Fwith further outbreaks of light
OL,8,Fdrizzle, however some heavier bursts
OL,9,Fare possible in the west during the
OL,10,Fsecond half of the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA cloudy day on Sunday with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of light rain and drizzle
OL,14,Fwhere the cloud thickens. A few
OL,15,Fbrighter spells possible in the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Near normal temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
